g.text: <left>: The left-hand side edge of an equation. See
an extension point for stripe skipping as well as specializations of the left-hand side tag
<right>: The right-hand side edge of an equation. See
an extension point for stripe skipping as well as specializations of the right-hand side tag
The main section of equations contains a pair of edges, a left-hand side edge and a right-hand side edge.
equations have orientation as an attribute.
